{"tid":248983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 真三國無雙•斬 (46) 服裝王異做乜L","createTime":"2017-05-19T03:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T15:34:57.000Z","uid":15940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b69fea5ea98b102cb521a565926b4033dafec6b","tid":248983,"uid":15940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>秒經必睇</strong></span></span><br />\n1. 升左lv先買成長禮包 拎唔拎得番之前個啲&amp;nbsp;<br />\n拎得番 可以一次過幾連10抽<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔啱屬既5-6星練唔練好<br />\n有愛可練 無愛可食<br />\n<br />\n3. 入坑前請三思 (不再補圖，因為冇人再敢抽)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0uqlw1s6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0uqlw1s6&h=21ab629b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uwnav1p8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuwnav1p8&h=6b35992d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 有用資料(轉巴哈)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=30635&amp;snA=635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D30635%26snA%3D635&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4c6dd12d\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=30635&amp;snA=635</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 修羅5-8擊破木桶成就<br />\n一開始係下面 唔好開自動行<br />\n<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">估計</span>只有三星通關先會掉武將<br />\n有試過唔係既巴打請糾正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>名將list及解說</strong></span></span><br />\n水:曹操 許褚 司馬懿 王元姬<br />\n木:諸葛亮 關羽 張飛 黃忠<br />\n火:呂布 孫策 大喬<br />\n<br />\n抽中岩屬=名將&amp;nbsp;<br />\n名將入手只可用元寶抽 (&lt;1%)<br />\n<br />\n抽中銀底<br />\n能力都會好過部份金底3/4*<br />\n不過好難升技 所以唔建議新手養<br />\n<br />\nbtw 602=呂布個女<br />\n(屌講左10尻幾次真係唔好再問，呢句生化吉兒講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>by中大貓奴</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>銀底名將數值係同4星金底將1樣<br />\n所以只計數值既話<br />\n金底名將&gt;銀底名將=金底4星將&gt;金底3星將</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">by波追人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>玉抽最勁可以抽到啱屬 3 星武將，例如周泰咁<br />\n滿技都好撚好打架。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">by問學人</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f903cc1137cad4744443fa6b8e725dd8f1c92906","tid":248983,"uid":15940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">裝備升級</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1rc3rd8hylRhK9bIXv8790ctIQuGeDtiEHJ1MlKtyaq8/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1rc3rd8hylRhK9bIXv8790ctIQuGeDtiEHJ1MlKtyaq8%2Fhtmlview&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=10f349fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1rc3rd8hylRhK9bIXv8790ctIQuGeDtiEHJ1MlKtyaq8/htmlview</a><br />\n<br />\n關於裝備滿等花費（按上面條link 做標準）：<br />\n<br />\n2星+20（3060 exp)（1件@$200）:<br />\n1:   11個1星 x $200=$2200<br />\n2:   5個1星+20（@$500）x$200 = $2900 <br />\n所以要2星滿等（+20）齋食1星就得。<br />\n<br />\n3星+20（4975 exp) (1件@400）<br />\n1: 4個2星+20（@$2200) x $400 = $10400<br />\n2: (8個2星 + 1個1星） x $400 = $3600<br />\n3: (4個3星 + 2個2星 + 1個1星）x $400 = $2800<br />\n<br />\n4星+20（7600 exp) (1件@800）<br />\n1: 13個2星 x $800 = $10400<br />\n2: (7個3星 + 1個2星) x $800 = $6400<br />\n3: 5個4星 x $800 = $4000<br />\n<br />\n5星+20 (24090 exp) (1件@1600)<br />\n1: (40個2星 + 1個1星) x $1600  = $65600<br />\n2: (24個3星 + 1個1星) x $1600 = $40000<br />\n3: (16個4星 + 1個1星) x $1600 = $27200<br />\n<br />\nps. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上面個表無6星所以無計，<br />\n但由此可見，食空等星既裝係會抵屌好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比各位巴打參考下，有錯請指出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>by生命裡那女孩</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a9e3f6495bf48bb71f1e6601efc22e81256a4c7b","tid":248983,"uid":15940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"1001又唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc303cf18078706043f53bbe2b05e69ac6c00d0","tid":248983,"uid":20185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1001又唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家都等緊你<br />\n<br />\nbtw早菲幾秒前都開左"},{"pid":"2932b1ddaae5eaa64b108fe07fa0ddc01191ad76","tid":248983,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"馬超肥刷邊關好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c26182997f8582cb92be791695d2c0a46446237","tid":248983,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"無追post.想問<br />\n唔係今日派野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}